<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style type="text/css">
    body, table, td, a { -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
    img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f5f7; margin: 0; padding: 0; width: 100% !important; }
    .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #dc2626); padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -1px; text-decoration: none; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.6; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    p { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 16px; }
    .otp-code { font-family: monospace; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; color: #dc2626; background: #fee2e2; border: 1px dashed #fca5a5; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 30px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff !important; background-color: #dc2626; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
    .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="logo">NexaStore</a>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your NexaStore account.</p>
      <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete the verification. This code is valid for {{expiryMinutes}} minutes:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
      </div>
      <p>Alternatively, click the link below to reset your password directly:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn" target="_blank">Reset Password</a>
      </div>
      <p>If you did not request this password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have security concerns.</p>
      <p>Thank you,<br>The NexaStore Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; 2026 NexaStore. All rights reserved.<br>
      This email is confidential and intended solely for the account holder.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
